_sText:
This is my very first map. There is 5 floors. 1 floor is secretplace. Full of AWPs, Second floor is full of AK47s, Third floor spawn and secret place in middle, fourth floor full of M4A1, and fifth floor full of HeGrenades.

Figure out how to get into secret areas ;) in the middle of third floor is buyzone.

Install: Drag and drop .bsp file into your Counter-Strike Source map foldier.

There is lots of lights so it may lag if u have bad computer. :)
